::Zardus::

Zardus looks at Liono Prime as the predacons depart. "Negotiations don't go 
well with rudeness," he says in his deadly voice, "Very well, I shall go help 
Hell Beast with his base. Untill next time."

With that Zardus turns around, and, motioning Nemesis to follow him, flies 
off toward the predacon base.
